metadata.name: Belarusian Metamorphosis
metadata.description:
S.O.S. for people from Belarus,
for not being sold to RUSSIA Emperor!
People want fair elections without a ARMS in your head for your vote!
STOP WAR, STOP NUCLEAR WEAPONS.

WE ARE SLAVES OF 2 DICTATORS!!!

Painting painted on 2020 for fair elections in Belarus, that  still current today with the new Ucraine - Russia war.
Lukashenko, artwork's protagonist, is a Belarusian dictator for the last 26 years. 

As an artist, I have the opportunity to express millions of stories against human rights, in one image.
133 x 92cm- Acrylics on canvas

It would be a Support if you share this content with others.
